    <div id="home_statement">
     <p>
      <span class="lead_in">
       The Sustainable 2nd Century
      </span>
      celebrates UC Davis’ long-term commitment to environmental, economic and social sustainability. We use our strengths in teaching, research and public service to address society’s most pressing problems. Ideas that start on our campus — powered by faculty, students and staff — transform the world.
      <a href="about/our_sustainable_2nd_century.html" title="Learn more about our Sustainable 2nd Century">
       Learn more...
      </a>
     </p>
